import React from 'react'
import { useForm } from 'react-hook-form'
import { TextField } from '@material-ui/core'
import Navbar from '../components/navbar'
import Container from '@material-ui/core/Container'


type Inputs = {
	name: string,
	composer: string,
	type: string,
	key: string,
	abc: string,

}
export default function TuneForm() {
	const { register, handleSubmit, watch, errors } = useForm<Inputs>()
	const onSubmit = (data: Inputs) => console.log(data)
	console.log(watch("Add a tune"))
	return (
		<>
			<Navbar/>
			<Container>
				<form onSubmit={handleSubmit(onSubmit)}>
					<TextField name="name" label="Name" ref={register({required: true})}/>
					<TextField name="composer" label="Composer" ref={register({required: true})}/>
					<TextField name="type" label="Type" ref={register({required: true})}/>
					<TextField name="key" label="Key" ref={register({required: true})}/>
					<TextField name="abc" label="abc" ref={register({required: true})}/>
				</form>
			</Container>
		</>
	)
}
